    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">Мерос мол-мулкни хатлаш далолатномаси </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Далолатнома тузилган нотариал идора номи </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Далолатнома тузилган сана</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Далолатномани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора жойлашган манзил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да жойлашган </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Далолатномани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора номи ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> нотариал идора</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;\"> </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Далолатнома тузилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда мен – Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Далолатномани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора номи ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нотариуси </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Далолатномани тасдиқлаган нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> Ўзбекистон Республикасининг «Нотариат тўғрисида»ги қонунининг 54-моддасига мувофиқ, манфаатдор шахслар:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">мерос қолдирувчининг болалари – </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Мерос қолдирувчининг биринчи фарзандининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи – </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Мерос қолдирувчининг биринчи фарзандининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Мерос қолдирувчининг биринчи фарзандининг паспорт серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#14}Мерос қолдирувчининг биринчи фарзандига паспорт берган ИИБ номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Мерос қолдирувчининг биринчи фарзандига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган), </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Мерос қолдирувчининг иккинчи фарзандининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи – </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17} Мерос қолдирувчининг иккинчи фарзандининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Мерос қолдирувчининг иккинчи фарзандининг паспорт серияси ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#19}Мерос қолдирувчининг иккинчи фарзандига паспорт берган ИИБ номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#20}Мерос қолдирувчининг иккинчи фарзандига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">мерос қолдирувчининг турмуш ўртоғи – <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#21}Мерос қолдирувчининг турмуш ўртоғининг манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи – </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#22} Мерос қолдирувчининг турмуш ўртоғининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#23}Мерос қолдирувчининг турмуш ўртоғининг паспорт серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#24}Мерос қолдирувчининг турмуш ўртоғига паспорт берган ИИБ номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#25}Мерос қолдирувчининг турмуш ўртоғига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">гувоҳлар – </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#26}Биринчи гувоҳнинг манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи – </span><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#27}Биринчи гувоҳнинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-28\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#28}Биринчи гувоҳнинг паспорт серияси ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-29\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#29}Биринчи гувоҳга паспорт берган ИИБ номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-30\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#30}Биринчи гувоҳга паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган), </span><span class=\"structures structure-31\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#31}Иккинчи гувоҳнинг манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи – </span><span class=\"structures structure-32\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#32}Иккинчи гувоҳнинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-33\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#33}Иккинчи гувоҳнинг паспорт серияси ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-34\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#34}Иккинчи гувоҳга паспорт берган ИИБ номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-35\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#35}Иккинчи гувоҳга паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган) иштирокида меросхўр </span><span class=\"structures structure-37\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#37}Мерос мол-мулкни қўриқлаш чора-тадбирларини кўриш тўғрисида ариза берган меросхўрнинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> нинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-38\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#38}Мерос мол-мулкни қўриқлаш чора-тадбирларини кўриш тўғрисида ариза берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда мерос мол-мулкни қўриқлаш чора-тадбирларини кўриш тўғрисида келиб тушган аризасига ва Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 1144-моддаси, Ўзбекистон Республикасининг «Нотариат тўғрисида»ги қонунининг 89-моддасига асосан </span><span class=\"structures structure-39\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#39}Мерос қолдирувчи яшаб келган манзил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> манзилида яшаган, </span><span class=\"structures structure-41\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#41}Мерос қолдирувчининг вафот этган санаси </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда вафот этган </span><span class=\"structures structure-40\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#40}Мерос қолдирувчининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг вафотидан сўнг қолган мерос мол-мулкни хатлаш далолатномасини туздик.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Хатлаш </span><span class=\"structures structure-42\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#42}Хатлов амалга оширилган манзил </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> манзилида жойлашган уйда амалга оширилди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Нотариус ушбу уй-жойга келишидан олдин турар-жой ёпилиб, муҳрланмаган, унда марҳумнинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-44\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#44}Хатлов ўтказилаётган уй-жойда марҳумнинг яшаб келаётган қариндоши (ўғли, қизи, турмуш ўртоғи ва ҳоказо)</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-45\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#45}Марҳумнинг хатлов ўтказилаётган уй-жойда яшаб келаётган қариндошининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> яшаб келмоқда.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мол-мулкнинг эскириш фоизини ҳисобга олган ҳолда унинг баҳоси тарафларнинг ўзаро келишувига кўра кўрсатилган.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мазкур далолатнома уч нусхада тузилди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Хатлаш далолатномасини тузган пайтда иштирок этган шахслар имзолари:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Нотариус: <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Далолатномани тасдиқлаган нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>______ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Гувоҳлар: <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#27}Биринчи гувоҳнинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>_______ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-32\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#32}Иккинчи гувоҳнинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>_______ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Манфаатдор шахслар: </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Мерос қолдирувчининг биринчи фарзандининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> _____ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Мерос қолдирувчининг иккинчи фарзандининг Ф.И.О <span class=\"leading\"></span>_____ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мерос қолдирувчининг турмуш ўртоғи: </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#22}Мерос қолдирувчининг турмуш ўртоғининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>_____ <span class=\"leading\"></span>(имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Хатлашда кўрсатилган пул жамғармаси, яъни </span><span class=\"structures structure-46\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#46}Мерос қолдирувчидан қолган ва хатлаш давомида хатланган пул миқдори </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм нотариус томонидан депозитга қўйиш учун олиб қўйилган.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Хатлаш далолатномасини тузган пайтда иштирок этган шахслар имзолари:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Нотариус: <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Далолатномани тасдиқлаган нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>______ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Гувоҳлар: <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#27}Биринчи гувоҳнинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>_______ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-32\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#32}Иккинчи гувоҳнинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>_______ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Манфаатдор шахслар:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Мерос қолдирувчининг биринчи фарзандининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span>_______ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Мерос қолдирувчининг иккинчи фарзандининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span>_______ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мерос қолдирувчининг турмуш ўртоғи: <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#22}Мерос қолдирувчининг турмуш ўртоғининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">_______ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Хатлаш далолатномасида кўрсатилган барча мол-мулклар мерос қолдирувчининг </span><span class=\"structures structure-44\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#44}Хатлов ўтказилаётган уй-жойда марҳумнинг яшаб келаётган қариндоши (ўғли, қизи, турмуш ўртоғи ва ҳоказо) </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-45\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#45}Марҳумнинг хатлов ўтказилаётган уй-жойда яшаб келаётган қариндошининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ихтиёрида сақлаш учун қолдирилди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-45\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#45}Марҳумнинг хатлов ўтказилаётган уй-жойда яшаб келаётган қариндошининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> Ўзбекистон Республикаси Жиноят кодексининг 167-моддаси ва бошқа тегишли моддаларига биноан мерос мол-мулкни талон-тарож қилганлик, бошқа шахсга берганлик ёки яширганлик ва меросхўрларга зарар етказганлик учун жавобгарлик тўғрисида огоҳлантирилсин.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-45\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#45}Марҳумнинг хатлов ўтказилаётган уй-жойда яшаб келаётган қариндошининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> _____ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Реестрга </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#4}Далолатноманинг реестр рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-сон билан қайд қилинди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Давлат божи </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ундириладиган давлат божи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Нотариус: <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Далолатномани тасдиқлаган нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>_______ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Далолатноманинг бир нусхасини қабул қилдим: </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-45\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#45}Марҳумнинг хатлов ўтказилаётган уй-жойда яшаб келаётган қариндошининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> _______ (имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
